TYPE MATERIAL. — Holotype : NHMW 1870 /0033/0005a (see Harzhauser & Landau 2016 : fig. 8F 1 - F 5 ). TYPE LOCALITY. — Lăpugiu de Sus ( Romania ), Langhian. STRATIGRAPHIC RANGE. — Langhian of Paratethys (see Harzhauser & Landau [2016] for detailed references), Serravallian of Karaman Basin ( Turkey ), Tortonian of Italy ( Montegibbio , see
Davoli [1972]
) and Greece ( Messara Basin , Crete ). MATERIAL EXAMINED. — Filippi : Nine specimens AMPG( IV ) 2651-2659;? Filippi , Crete : 30 specimens ( MNHN .F. A72606 to MNHN .F. A72635 ). All specimens display a colour pattern under UV light.

